column5: Any reports on walleyes and Crappie fishing in the nestor falls area heading up in 15 days

Scott: Lots of changes can occur in 15 days. Post your inquiry closer to the time you leave. You should be able to get some up-to-date info on walleyes and crappie. I with I could help you, but almost exclusively fish for muskies and northern. OK....some smallies and lake trout, too.
I'll give it a try later next week. Thanks Scott
